data.description: You do not want to miss this immaculate 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 car garage townhome located in the gated "Boyette Park" community of Riverview. Only 2 years old, this Mattamy "Venice" model townhome has over 2,600 heated sq ft, features lots of upgrades and shows like a model. Once you walk through the front door, you will feel the openness to this townhome with the 9' ceilings and 8' doors. Wood look tile is in all the main living areas on the first floor along with neutral colored carpet upstairs and in the first floor bedroom. The kitchen is in the heart of the home and boasts a walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, tiled backsplash, and an island with undermount sink, swan neck faucet, & pendant lights. Large sliders lead from the living room to the pavered porch area that is covered and screened in. There is a single bedroom on the first floor with its own bathroom that is perfect for out of town guests. Upstairs you will find an enormous bonus room that is great for families and movie nights. The generous sized master bedroom has a tray ceiling and a huge walk-in closet. His/hers vanities, along with a tiled walk-in shower and soaking tub pull together the master bathroom. The 2 guest bedrooms upstairs are separated by the loft and share a bathroom with dual sinks, granite counters, and a tub/shower. All guest bedrooms feature walk-in closets. Upgraded ceiling fans throughout the home. Boyette Park is a gated community that offers low-maintenance paired villas, town homes and distinctive single-family homes. This premier location is close schools, recreation, shopping and 75. The community offers an area with covered space out by the pool and a BBQ area, resort-style zero-entry pool with lap lane, expansive outdoor social areas, and playground. Schedule your personal showing NOW!!
